1 Section 1. It is the intent of the Legislature to implement a net
2 reduction of five million two hundred thousand dollars of General Funds
3 for fiscal year 2026-27 for the Department of Correctional Services to
4 Program 200, Operations, from the McCook Detention Facility.
5 It is the intent of the Legislature that the Department of
6 Correctional Services use five million dollars of General Funds for
7 fiscal year 2026-27 for tuition, fees, and other direct costs for reentry
8 and reintegration programming for committed offenders.
